                            <comment id="246955" author="adilger" created="Fri, 10 May 2019 07:47:14 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This appears to be failing only on ZFS.  The first similar failure that I could find was on 2018-06-12  with patch &lt;a href=&quot;https://review.whamcloud.com/31976&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://review.whamcloud.com/31976&lt;/a&gt; &quot;&lt;tt&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-11310&quot; title=&quot;support for SLES 15&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-11310&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-11310&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; tests: for test.&lt;/tt&gt;&quot;, though this is a test patch for SLES15 ldiskfs that never landed, so it is possible there was something wrong with that kernel/patch?&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/772bbf04-6dec-11e8-a522-52540065bddc&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/772bbf04-6dec-11e8-a522-52540065bddc&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The next failure is on 2018-08-09 with patch &lt;a href=&quot;https://review.whamcloud.com/31504&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://review.whamcloud.com/31504&lt;/a&gt; v19 &quot;&lt;tt&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-4684&quot; title=&quot;DNE3: allow migrating DNE striped directory&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-4684&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-4684&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; lmv: support accessing migrating directory&lt;/tt&gt;&quot;, which eventually landed on 2018-10-01, which is after the &lt;em&gt;next&lt;/em&gt; failure on 2018-08-23, so that could not have been the patch that introduced the problem.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I&apos;d be inclined to look for a patch that landed just before 2018-08-09 (there was a big batch of landings on 2018-08-06), which has patch &lt;a href=&quot;https://review.whamcloud.com/32827&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://review.whamcloud.com/32827&lt;/a&gt; &quot;&lt;tt&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-11153&quot; title=&quot;the uninitialized variable &amp;quot;ver&amp;quot; could be used in qmt_set&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-11153&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-11153&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; quota: initialize ver for default quota&lt;/tt&gt;&quot; among others, and more on 2018-08-09.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="246867" author="guzheng" created="Thu, 9 May 2019 01:41:37 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Another instance failed on test_2:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/71c71570-71ad-11e9-bd0e-52540065bddc&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/71c71570-71ad-11e9-bd0e-52540065bddc&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
